snippet.title: Exception Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Exception launches August 13 on Steam and console (Switch / Xbox One / PS4)

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/456390/Exception/

Pre-purchase on Switch:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/exception-switch/

Pre-purchase on Xbox One:
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/exception/bssklhhh96ds

Official Website:
http://exceptiongame.com/


Music by Street Cleaner featured in the Exception soundtrack:
https://streetcleaner.bandcamp.com/
